              <history-note id="DLM1490317"><amended-provision>Section 26(2)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 August 2008</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM1313622">section 50(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Land Transport Management Amendment Act 2008</amending-leg> (2008 No 47).</history-note>
            </history>
